<item>
            <title>[LU-19279] Include root FID in debugfs MDT exports</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19279</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When clients mount Lustre, the root FID is stored in the client export on the MDT0, which reflects the subdirectory that is currently mounted by the client. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems beneficial to expose this information on the MDT server-side through debugfs &lt;tt&gt;mdt.TARGET.exports.NID.export&lt;/tt&gt;. This allows administrators to verify which subdirectory a client has mounted, even if access to the client is not possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
